=== Weekly Schedule ===
----Play Ball Game | Funds -6; Mood -1; Fitness +5

Play with Wooden Blocks | Funds -6; Mood -1; Dexterity +5

Read | Funds -6; Mood -1; Knowledge +5

Have a Think | Funds -6; Mood -1; Sensitivity +5

Dance Practice | Mood +3

Do House Work | Funds + 8



=== Go Outside ===
----

==== Sightseeing ====
Spend AP to recover Mood. 

==== Experiences ====
Spend AP to gain Funds. 

==== Events ====
Spend action points to encounter random events at specific locations. 

* Academy
* Souvenir Shop
* Cafe
* Seaside Park
* Hardware Store 
* Diner 
* Gastronomy District
* Tranquil Summit
* Sports Ground 
* World of Wonder

==== Ship Girl Quests ====
New Jersey - Outgoing | New Jersey Blessing - Dexterity activities consume -50% Mood. 

Sirius - Shy | Sirius Blessing - Knowledge activities consume -50% Mood.  

De Zeven Provincien - Outgoing | Blessing - Sensitivity activities consume -50% Mood.  

Epee - Shy | Epee Blessing - When shopping at the Fortune Teller, Funds spent -10%  

Tashkent- Outgoing | Tashkent Blessing - Fitness activities consume -50% Mood.   

Noshiro - Shy | Noshiro's Blessing - At turn start, if Mood <70, Mood +20. If Mood is 70 or higher, +25(fixed) to all stats.     

