=== Endings ===
----

After 20 turns you are presented with a set of endings that Lora is eligible for depending on what you did during the playthrough. 

To achieve the Pianist or Botanist ending, you must complete an event chain for each. These are marked on the '''Go Outside''' map with an orange ! symbol.  
